title: the code
pid: f8819956-0c62-442d-b186-7835f1c2d5a8
body: |2-
  `_factor n m` returns `m / n` if it makes sense.
  Embed has to do the reverse.
    _Factor :: Int -> Prism' Int Int
    _Factor n = prism' embed match
     where
      embed :: Int -> Int
      embed i = i * n
      match :: Int -> Maybe Int
      match i
        | i `mod` n == 0 = Just (i `div` n)
        | otherwise = Nothing
